from 5 to 10 pages and from 5 to 10 minutes. The text of the amendment identifies each of the changes to the fees. The NASD
is requesting that the amendment be implemented on May 1, 1994.

The NASD believes that the proposed rule change is consistent with the provisions of Section 15A(b)(5) of the Act,
